MainText: I am a software development student at the IT-University of Copenhagen in Denmark and a freelance developer.
AboutText:
I create software solutions for companies and people, who want to improve their work-processes with IT. I focus on making IT as easy and simple to use - and showing that IT can help in many ways.
 I write code in a lot of languages but mainly focus on C# and F#.

ServicesCollection.Title: .NET
ServicesCollection.Description: A lot of experience with Microsoft's .NET platform and C# and F#

ServicesCollection.Title: Native Apps
ServicesCollection.Description: Responsive native apps for Windows 7 and 8 PCs as well as all Windows 10 devices.

ServicesCollection.Title: Into the Cloud
ServicesCollection.Description: I allow multiple services to talk together allowing you and your team to work together to solve your problems.

ServicesCollection.Title: Collaboration with You
ServicesCollection.Description: Collaborating with you makes sure that we reach the best solution together!
